data.description: Check out this Move-In-Ready ranch in the Northridge neighborhood! Conveniently located just off 27th and Interstate 80, you're close to all the shopping and dining the area has to offer! Upon entry you'll be greeted by an open concept living room, dining area and kitchen. Offering great sight lines so you never miss out on that nail biter Husker football game (National Champs this year right?!?). Also on the main floor is 2 generously sized bedrooms, a full bathroom and your primary bedroom with an attached full bathroom as well! Laundry is also on the main level. Downstairs you'll find a VERY large 2nd living area / den offering all kinds of opportunity to make our own. You'll also find a 3rd full bathroom, a 4th bedroom along with 2 unfinished storage areas. In the back yard you'll find a nice deck and a fully fenced in back yard. Spot (your fur baby) will love it! Schedule your showing today!
